# Language cheat sheet

This language follows the basic [markdown syntax](https://www.markdownguide.org/cheat-sheet/) but adds some extras like formulas, code, HTML and custom space.

## Headers

# H1

...

###### H6

## Style

_italics_

**bold**

**_bold and italics_**

_**italics and bold**_

